<lb n="0910b07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0910b08" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1467</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0910b09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><anchor type="circle"/><note n="0910006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此經聖本大異今附卷末，〔佛說〕－【聖乙】</note><note n="0910006" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->佛說【大】，〔－〕【聖乙】，此經聖本大異今附卷末</note><cb:jhead><title>佛說犯戒罪<note n="0910007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔報〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">報【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910007"><lem wit="【大】">報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>輕重經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0910b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0910b11" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0910008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後漢安息三藏安世高譯＝出在目蓮問毘尼經後秦安世高譯【聖乙】</note><note n="0910008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後漢安息三藏安世高譯【大】，出在目蓮問毘尼經後秦安世高譯【聖乙】</note><app n="0910008"><lem wit="【大】">後漢安息三藏安世高<note n="0910009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譯＋（漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非）夾註【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯【大】，譯(漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非)【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910009"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">譯<note place="inline">漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">出在目蓮問毘尼經後秦安世高譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0910b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT24p0910b1201">如是我聞：</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b1205" cb:place="inline">一時佛住王舍城迦蘭陀竹園。爾
<lb n="0910b13" ed="T"/>時尊者<note n="0910010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目連＝大目犍連【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目連【大】，大目犍連【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910010"><lem wit="【大】">目連</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大目犍連</rdg></app>，晡<note n="0910011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【宮】</note><note n="0910011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0910011"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>從禪定覺，往至<note n="0910012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世尊【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910012"><lem wit="【大】">世尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0910b14" ed="T"/><note n="0910013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋所【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，佛所【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910013"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛所</rdg></app>，頭面禮足<note n="0910014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔却住一面〕－【宮】</note><note n="0910014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">却住一面【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0910014"><lem wit="【大】">却<note n="0910015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝坐【三】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住【大】，坐【宋】【元】【明】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910015"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖乙】">坐</rdg></app>一面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0910016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時尊者大目連＝合掌恭敬而【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時尊者大目連【大】，合掌恭敬而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910016"><lem wit="【大】">時尊者大目連</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">合掌恭敬而</rdg></app>
<lb n="0910b15" ed="T"/>白佛言：「世尊！意有所疑，今欲請問。<note n="0910017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】＊，惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910017"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>願聽
<lb n="0910b16" ed="T"/>許。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b1602" cb:place="inline">佛告目連：「<note n="0910018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聽＝恣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽【大】，恣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910018"><lem wit="【大】">聽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恣</rdg></app>汝所問。當為汝說。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b1614" cb:place="inline">目連即
<lb n="0910b17" ed="T"/>白佛言：「世尊！若比丘、比丘尼，無慚愧<note n="0910019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【宮】</note><note n="0910019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0910019"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，輕
<lb n="0910b18" ed="T"/>慢佛語，犯眾學戒，如是犯波羅提提舍尼、波
<lb n="0910b19" ed="T"/><note n="0910020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝逸【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，逸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910020"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】">逸</rdg></app>提、偷蘭遮、僧伽婆尸沙、<note n="0910021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（犯）＋波【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波【大】，犯波【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910021"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">犯波</rdg></app>羅夷，得幾
<lb n="0910b20" ed="T"/><note n="0910022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910022"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不饒益罪？<app type="star" corresp="#0910017"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>願解說。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b2010" cb:place="inline">佛告目連：「諦聽諦
<lb n="0910b21" ed="T"/>聽。<note n="0910023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝今【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，今【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910023"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">今</rdg></app>為汝說。若比丘、比丘尼無慚無愧，輕
<lb n="0910b22" ed="T"/>慢佛<note n="0910024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝說【聖乙】</note><note n="0910024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語【大】，說【聖乙】</note><app n="0910024"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">說</rdg></app>，犯眾學戒。如四天王<note n="0910025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910025"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>壽五百歲
<lb n="0910b23" ed="T"/>墮泥犁中，於人間數九百千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b2313" cb:place="inline"><note n="0910026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛告＝復次【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛告【大】＊，復次【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910026"><lem wit="【大】">佛告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復次</rdg></app>目連：
<lb n="0910b24" ed="T"/>「<note n="0910027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若）＋無慚【三】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><note n="0910027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無慚【大】＊，若無慚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><app n="0910027"><lem wit="【大】">無慚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】">若無慚</rdg></app><note n="0910028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><note n="0910028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><app n="0910028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愧，輕慢佛語，犯波羅提提舍尼。如
<lb n="0910b25" ed="T"/>三十三天壽<note n="0910029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910029"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>千歲墮泥<note n="0910b2501" resp="CBETA" type="add">犁【CB】，梨【大】</note><app n="0910b2501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">犁</lem><rdg wit="【大】">梨</rdg></app>中，於人間數三
<lb n="0910b26" ed="T"/>億六十千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b2606" cb:place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0910026"><lem wit="【大】">佛告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復次</rdg></app>目連：「<anchor xml:id="fxT24p0910b03"/>無慚<app type="star" corresp="#0910028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愧，輕慢佛
<lb n="0910b27" ed="T"/>語，犯波<note n="0910030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝逸【聖乙】</note><note n="0910030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，逸【聖乙】</note><app n="0910030"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">逸</rdg></app>提。如<note n="0910031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝焰【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，焰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910031"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】">焰</rdg></app>摩天壽二千歲，墮泥犁
<lb n="0910b28" ed="T"/>中，於人間數二<note n="0910032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＋（四）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，十四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910032"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十四</rdg></app>億四十千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910b2813" cb:place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0910026"><lem wit="【大】">佛告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復次</rdg></app>目連：
<lb n="0910b29" ed="T"/>「<anchor xml:id="fxT24p0910b06"/>無慚<app type="star" corresp="#0910028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愧，輕慢佛語，犯偷蘭遮。如兜率天
<pb n="0910c" ed="T" xml:id="T24.1467a.0910c"/>
<lb n="0910c01" ed="T"/>壽四千歲墮泥犁中，於人間數五十億六十
<lb n="0910c02" ed="T"/>千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910c0203" cb:place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0910026"><lem wit="【大】">佛告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復次</rdg></app>目連：「<anchor xml:id="fxT24p0910c02"/>無慚<app type="star" corresp="#0910028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愧，輕慢佛語，犯
<lb n="0910c03" ed="T"/>僧伽婆尸沙。如不憍樂天壽八千歲，墮泥犁
<lb n="0910c04" ed="T"/>中，於人間數二百三十億四十千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910c0415" cb:place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0910026"><lem wit="【大】">佛告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復次</rdg></app>
<lb n="0910c05" ed="T"/>目連：「<anchor xml:id="fxT24p0910c05"/>無慚<app type="star" corresp="#0910028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>愧，輕慢佛語，犯波羅夷。如他
<lb n="0910c06" ed="T"/>化自在天壽十六千歲墮泥犁中，於人間數
<lb n="0910c07" ed="T"/>九百二十一億<note n="0910033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＝九【聖乙】</note><note n="0910033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六【大】，九【聖乙】</note><app n="0910033"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">九</rdg></app>十千歲。」</p><p xml:id="pT24p0910c0711" cb:place="inline"><note n="0910034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910034"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>尊者目連聞
<lb n="0910c08" ed="T"/>佛所說歡喜奉行。</p>
<lb n="0910c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT24p0910c0901">爾時<note n="0910035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔尊者〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊者【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910035"><lem wit="【大】">尊者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>目連即說偈言：</p>
<lb n="0910c10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT24p0910c1001" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「因緣輕慢故，</l><l>命終墮惡道；</l>
<lb n="0910c11" ed="T"/><l>因緣修善<note n="0910036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝故【宮】</note><note n="0910036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，故【宮】</note><app n="0910036"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">故</rdg></app>，</l><l>於此生天上。</l>
<lb n="0910c12" ed="T"/><l>緣斯<note n="0910037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修福業＝善業故【聖乙】</note><note n="0910037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">修福業【大】，善業故【聖乙】</note><app n="0910037"><lem wit="【大】">修<note n="0910038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福【大】，善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910038"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善</rdg></app>業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">善業故</rdg></app>，</l><l>離惡得解脫；</l>
<lb n="0910c13" ed="T"/><l>不善觀因緣，</l><l>身壞<note n="0910039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入惡道＝墮惡趣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入惡道【大】，墮惡趣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910039"><lem wit="【大】">入惡道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">墮惡趣</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0910c14" ed="T"/><note n="0910040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（比丘…佛））二十四句百二十字＝（（為福受樂報所欲皆自然超逾生死流上家之涅槃若人為福者天神自然護所願皆疾成眾魔莫能壞））五言八句四十字【聖乙】</note><note n="0910040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（比丘…佛）百二十字【大】，為福受樂報所欲皆自然超逾生死流上家之涅槃若人為福者天神自然護所願皆疾成眾魔莫能壞【聖乙】</note><app n="0910040" cb:word-count="120"><lem wit="【大】"><l>比丘謹慎樂，</l><l>放逸多憂譴，</l>
<lb n="0910c15" ed="T"/><l>變諍小致大，</l><l>積惡入火<note n="0910041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𤆶＝焚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤆶【大】，焚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910041"><lem wit="【大】">𤆶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">焚</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0910c16" ed="T"/><l>持戒福致喜，</l><l>破戒有懼心，</l>
<lb n="0910c17" ed="T"/><l>永斷三界漏，</l><l>爾乃得涅槃。</l>
<lb n="0910c18" ed="T"/><l>戒德可恃怙，</l><l>福報常隨<note n="0910042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">己＝心【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">己【大】，心【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910042"><lem wit="【大】">己</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0910c19" ed="T"/><l>見法為人長，</l><l><note n="0910043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＝永【三】</note><note n="0910043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾【大】，永【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0910043"><lem wit="【大】">眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">永</rdg></app>遠三惡道。</l>
<lb n="0910c20" ed="T"/><l>戒慎除恐畏，</l><l>福德三界尊，</l>
<lb n="0910c21" ed="T"/><l>鬼龍<note n="0910044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蛇＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蛇【大】，邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910044"><lem wit="【大】">蛇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>毒害，</l><l><note n="0910045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不犯持戒人∞神仙五通人【宋】</note><note n="0910045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不犯持戒人【大】∞神仙五通人【宋】</note><app n="0910045"><lem wit="【大】">不犯持戒人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">神仙五通人</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0910c22" ed="T"/><l><note n="0910046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不犯持戒人∞神仙五通人【宋】</note><note n="0910046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神仙五通人【大】∞不犯持戒人【宋】</note><app n="0910046"><lem wit="【大】">神仙五通人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">不犯持戒人</rdg></app>，</l><l>造世諸呪術，</l>
<pb n="0911a" ed="T" xml:id="T24.1467a.0911a"/>
<lb n="0911a01" ed="T"/><l>為<note n="0911001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝彼【三】</note><note n="0911001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸【大】，彼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0911001"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">彼</rdg></app>慚愧者，</l><l>斷諸無慚愧。</l>
<lb n="0911a02" ed="T"/><l>如來制禁戒，</l><l>半月半月說，</l>
<lb n="0911a03" ed="T"/><l>已說戒利益，</l><l>稽首禮諸佛。」</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】">為福受樂報所欲皆自然超逾生死流上家之涅槃若人為福者天神自然護所願皆疾成眾魔莫能壞</rdg></app></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0911a04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><note n="0911002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說犯戒罪報輕重經〕－【聖乙】</note><note n="0911002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說犯戒罪報輕重經【大】，〔－〕【聖乙】</note><app n="0911002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說犯戒罪<app type="star" corresp="#0910007"><lem wit="【大】">報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>輕重經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
